videoSnippet.title: Vidit Gujrathi Takes Down Captain America! | Gujrathi vs Shankland | Danzhou (2018)
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator Follow me on Instagram for extra content: https://www.instagram.com/agadmator/

The 9th edition of the Danzhou Super Grandmaster Tournament is taking place from 27 July to 3 August 2018 in Danzhou on the South China Sea island province of Hainan. This year the 8-player single round-robin features five international grandmasters as well as some top Chinese players.

The total prize fund is $60,000, with 20,000 for 1st place. Players have 90 minutes for 40 moves then 30 minutes to the end of the game, with a 30-second increment from move 1. Official website: cca.imsa.cn

Vidit Gujrathi vs Sam Shankland
9th edition of the Danzhou Super Grandmaster Tournament (2018), anzhou on the South China Sea island province of Hainan, rd 3, Jul-30 
Slav Defense: Modern, Wuiet Variation (D11)
